{
  "video_id": "b0vDWqp6J7Y",
  "title": "The design genius of Charles + Ray Eames",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12160.0,
      "end_time": 15160.0,
      "text": "Charles and Ray were a team. They were husband and wife."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15160.0,
      "end_time": 18160.0,
      "text": "Despite the New York Times&#39; and Vanity Fair&#39;s best efforts recently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18160.0,
      "end_time": 20160.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re not brothers. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20160.0,
      "end_time": 22160.0,
      "text": "And they were a lot of fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22160.0,
      "end_time": 24160.0,
      "text": "You know, Ray was the one who wore the ampersands in the family."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24160.0,
      "end_time": 27160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27160.0,
      "end_time": 30160.0,
      "text": "We are going to focus on Charles today, because it is Charles&#39; 100th birthday."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30160.0,
      "end_time": 33160.0,
      "text": "But when I speak of him, I&#39;m really speaking of both of them as a team."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33160.0,
      "end_time": 36160.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s Charles when he was three. So he would be 100 this June."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36160.0,
      "end_time": 38160.0,
      "text": "We have a lot of cool celebrations that we&#39;re going to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38160.0,
      "end_time": 40160.0,
      "text": "The thing about their work"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40160.0,
      "end_time": 42160.0,
      "text": "is that most people come to the door of furniture --"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42160.0,
      "end_time": 44160.0,
      "text": "I suspect you probably recognize this chair"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44160.0,
      "end_time": 46160.0,
      "text": "and some of the others I&#39;m going to show you."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46160.0,
      "end_time": 49160.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;re going to first enter through the door of the Big Top."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 69160.0,
      "end_time": 71160.0,
      "text": "The whole thing about this, though, is that, you know, why am I showing it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 71160.0,
      "end_time": 73160.0,
      "text": "Is it because Charles and Ray made this film?"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 73160.0,
      "end_time": 77160.0,
      "text": "This is actually a training film for a clown college that they had."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 77160.0,
      "end_time": 80160.0,
      "text": "They also practiced a clown act when the future of furniture"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 80160.0,
      "end_time": 83160.0,
      "text": "was not nearly as auspicious as it turned out to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 83160.0,
      "end_time": 87160.0,
      "text": "There is a picture of Charles. So let&#39;s watch the next clip."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 87160.0,
      "end_time": 91160.0,
      "text": "The film that we&#39;re about to see is a film they made for the Moscow World&#39;s Fair."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 91160.0,
      "end_time": 93160.0,
      "text": "Video: This is the land."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 93160.0,
      "end_time": 95160.0,
      "text": "It has many contrasts."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 95160.0,
      "end_time": 99160.0,
      "text": "It is rough and it is flat."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 99160.0,
      "end_time": 101160.0,
      "text": "In places it is cold."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 101160.0,
      "end_time": 103160.0,
      "text": "In some it is hot."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 118160.0,
      "end_time": 121160.0,
      "text": "Too much rain falls on some areas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 121160.0,
      "end_time": 123160.0,
      "text": "and not enough on others."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 125160.0,
      "end_time": 128160.0,
      "text": "But people live on this land."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 128160.0,
      "end_time": 130160.0,
      "text": "And, as in Russia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 130160.0,
      "end_time": 134160.0,
      "text": "they are drawn together into towns and cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 134160.0,
      "end_time": 138160.0,
      "text": "Here is something of the way they live."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 138160.0,
      "end_time": 140160.0,
      "text": "Eames Demetrios: Now, this is a film that was hardly ever seen in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 140160.0,
      "end_time": 144160.0,
      "text": "It was on seven screens and it was 200 feet across."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 144160.0,
      "end_time": 146160.0,
      "text": "And it was at the height of the Cold War."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 146160.0,
      "end_time": 148160.0,
      "text": "The Nixon-Khrushchev Kitchen Debate"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 148160.0,
      "end_time": 150160.0,
      "text": "happened about 50 feet from where this was shown."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 150160.0,
      "end_time": 152160.0,
      "text": "And yet, how did it start?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 152160.0,
      "end_time": 154160.0,
      "text": "You know, commonality, the first line"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 154160.0,
      "end_time": 156160.0,
      "text": "in Charles&#39; narration was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 156160.0,
      "end_time": 158160.0,
      "text": "\"The same stars that shine down on Russia"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 158160.0,
      "end_time": 160160.0,
      "text": "shine down on the United States. From the sky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 160160.0,
      "end_time": 162160.0,
      "text": "our cities look much the same.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 162160.0,
      "end_time": 165160.0,
      "text": "It was that human connection that Charles and Ray always found in everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 165160.0,
      "end_time": 167160.0,
      "text": "And you can imagine, and the thing about it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 167160.0,
      "end_time": 170160.0,
      "text": "that they believed that the human mind could handle this number of images"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 170160.0,
      "end_time": 172160.0,
      "text": "because the important thing was to get the gestalt"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 172160.0,
      "end_time": 174160.0,
      "text": "of what the images were about."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 174160.0,
      "end_time": 176160.0,
      "text": "So that was just a little snip."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 176160.0,
      "end_time": 178160.0,
      "text": "But the thing about Charles and Ray"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 178160.0,
      "end_time": 180160.0,
      "text": "is that they were always modeling stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 180160.0,
      "end_time": 182160.0,
      "text": "They were always trying things out."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 182160.0,
      "end_time": 184160.0,
      "text": "I think one of the things I am passionate about, my grandparents work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 184160.0,
      "end_time": 186160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m passionate about my work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 186160.0,
      "end_time": 189160.0,
      "text": "but on top of all that I&#39;m passionate"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 189160.0,
      "end_time": 191160.0,
      "text": "about a holistic vision of design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 191160.0,
      "end_time": 194160.0,
      "text": "where design is a life skill, not a professional skill."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 194160.0,
      "end_time": 197160.0,
      "text": "And you know, those of us with kids often want our kids to take music."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 197160.0,
      "end_time": 199160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m no exception."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 199160.0,
      "end_time": 202160.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not about them becoming Bono or Tracy Chapman."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 202160.0,
      "end_time": 205160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about getting that music thing going through their heads and their thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 205160.0,
      "end_time": 208160.0,
      "text": "Design is the same way. Design has to become that same way."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 208160.0,
      "end_time": 210160.0,
      "text": "And this is a model that they did of that seven-screen presentation."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 210160.0,
      "end_time": 213160.0,
      "text": "And Charles just checking it out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 213160.0,
      "end_time": 215160.0,
      "text": "So now we&#39;re going to go through that door of furniture."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 215160.0,
      "end_time": 217160.0,
      "text": "This is an unusual installation of airport seating."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 217160.0,
      "end_time": 221160.0,
      "text": "So what we&#39;re going to see is some of the icons of Eames furniture."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 221160.0,
      "end_time": 224160.0,
      "text": "And the thing about their furniture is that they said the role of the designer"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 224160.0,
      "end_time": 226160.0,
      "text": "was essentially that of a good host,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 226160.0,
      "end_time": 228160.0,
      "text": "anticipating the needs of the guest."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 228160.0,
      "end_time": 230160.0,
      "text": "So those are cool images. But these are ones I think are really cool."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 230160.0,
      "end_time": 233160.0,
      "text": "These are all the prototypes. These are the mistakes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 233160.0,
      "end_time": 235160.0,
      "text": "although I don&#39;t think mistakes is the right word in design."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 235160.0,
      "end_time": 237160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just the things you try out"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 237160.0,
      "end_time": 239160.0,
      "text": "to kind of make it work better."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 239160.0,
      "end_time": 242160.0,
      "text": "And you know some of them would probably be terrible chairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 242160.0,
      "end_time": 245160.0,
      "text": "Some of them are kind of cool looking. It&#39;s like \"Hey, why didn&#39;t they try that?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 245160.0,
      "end_time": 247160.0,
      "text": "It was that hands-on iterative process"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 247160.0,
      "end_time": 250160.0,
      "text": "which is so much like vernacular design"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 250160.0,
      "end_time": 253160.0,
      "text": "and folk design in traditional cultures."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 253160.0,
      "end_time": 255160.0,
      "text": "And I think that&#39;s one of the commonalities between modernism"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 255160.0,
      "end_time": 258159.0,
      "text": "and traditional design. I think it may be a real common ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 258160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261160.00000000003,
      "text": "as we kind of figure out what on earth to do in the next 20 or 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 261160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263160.0,
      "text": "The other thing that&#39;s kind of cool is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 263160.0,
      "end_time": 266160.0,
      "text": "you look at this and in the media when people say design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 266160.0,
      "end_time": 268160.0,
      "text": "they actually mean style."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 268160.0,
      "end_time": 270160.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m really here to talk about design."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 270160.0,
      "end_time": 272160.0,
      "text": "But you know the object is just a pivot."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 272160.0,
      "end_time": 275160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a pivot between a process and a system."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 275160.0,
      "end_time": 279160.0,
      "text": "And this is a little film I made"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 279160.0,
      "end_time": 281160.0,
      "text": "about the making of the Eames lounge chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 281160.0,
      "end_time": 285160.0,
      "text": "The design process for Charles and Ray"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 285160.0,
      "end_time": 290160.0,
      "text": "never ended in manufacturing."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 290160.0,
      "end_time": 292160.0,
      "text": "It continued. They were always trying to make thing better and better."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 292160.0,
      "end_time": 297160.0,
      "text": "Because it&#39;s like as Bill Clinton was saying about Rwandan health clinics."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 297160.0,
      "end_time": 299160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not enough to create one."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 299160.0,
      "end_time": 301160.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve got to create a system that will work better and better."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 301160.0,
      "end_time": 303160.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ve always liked this prototype picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 303160.0,
      "end_time": 305160.0,
      "text": "Because it just kind of, you know, doesn&#39;t get any more basic than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 305160.0,
      "end_time": 307160.0,
      "text": "You try things out."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 307160.0,
      "end_time": 309160.0,
      "text": "This is a relatively famous chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 309160.0,
      "end_time": 312160.0,
      "text": "Its early version had an \"X\" base. That&#39;s what the collectors like."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 312160.0,
      "end_time": 314160.0,
      "text": "Charles and Ray liked this one because it was better."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 314160.0,
      "end_time": 317160.0,
      "text": "It worked better: \"H\" base, much more practical."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 317160.0,
      "end_time": 319160.0,
      "text": "This is something called a splint."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 319160.0,
      "end_time": 321160.0,
      "text": "And I was very touched by Dean Kamen&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 321160.0,
      "end_time": 325160.0,
      "text": "work for the military, or for the soldiers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 325160.0,
      "end_time": 329160.0,
      "text": "because Charles and Ray designed a molded plywood splint. This is it."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 329160.0,
      "end_time": 331160.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;d been working on furniture before."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 331160.0,
      "end_time": 334160.0,
      "text": "But doing these splints they learned a lot about the manufacturing process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 334160.0,
      "end_time": 337160.0,
      "text": "which was incredibly important to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 347160.0,
      "end_time": 349160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m trying to show you too much,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 349160.0,
      "end_time": 351160.0,
      "text": "because I want you to really get a broth of ideas and images."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 351160.0,
      "end_time": 353160.0,
      "text": "This is a house that Charles and Ray designed."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 353160.0,
      "end_time": 356160.0,
      "text": "My sister is chasing someone else. It&#39;s not me."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 356160.0,
      "end_time": 360160.0,
      "text": "Although I endorse heartily the fact that he stole her diary, it&#39;s not me."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 360160.0,
      "end_time": 364160.0,
      "text": "And then this is a film, on the lower left, that Charles and Ray made."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 364160.0,
      "end_time": 367160.0,
      "text": "Now look at that plastic chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 367160.0,
      "end_time": 369160.0,
      "text": "The house is 1949."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 369160.0,
      "end_time": 372160.0,
      "text": "The chair is done in 1949."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 372160.0,
      "end_time": 376160.0,
      "text": "Charles and Ray,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 376160.0,
      "end_time": 378160.0,
      "text": "they didn&#39;t obsess about style for it&#39;s own sake."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 378160.0,
      "end_time": 381160.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t say, \"Our style is curves. Let&#39;s make the house curvy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 381160.0,
      "end_time": 384160.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t say, \"Our style is grids. Let&#39;s make the chair griddy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 384160.0,
      "end_time": 386160.0,
      "text": "They focused on the need."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 386160.0,
      "end_time": 388160.0,
      "text": "They tried to solve the design problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 388160.0,
      "end_time": 391160.0,
      "text": "Charles used to say, \"The extent to which you have a design style"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 391160.0,
      "end_time": 393160.0,
      "text": "is the extent to which you have not solved the design problem.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 393160.0,
      "end_time": 395160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s kind of a brutal quote."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 395160.0,
      "end_time": 397160.0,
      "text": "This is the earlier design of that house."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 397160.0,
      "end_time": 399160.0,
      "text": "And again, they managed to figure out a way to make a prototype"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 399160.0,
      "end_time": 402160.0,
      "text": "of a house -- architecture, very expensive medium."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 402160.0,
      "end_time": 405160.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a film we&#39;ve been hearing things about."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 405160.0,
      "end_time": 408160.0,
      "text": "The \"Powers of Ten\" is a film they made."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 408160.0,
      "end_time": 410160.0,
      "text": "If we watch the next clip,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 410160.0,
      "end_time": 414160.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re going to see the first version of \"Powers of Ten,\" upper left."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 414160.0,
      "end_time": 418160.0,
      "text": "The familiar one on the lower right."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 418160.0,
      "end_time": 421160.0,
      "text": "The Eames&#39; film Tops, lower left."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 421160.0,
      "end_time": 424160.0,
      "text": "And a lamp that Charles designed for a church."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 424160.0,
      "end_time": 427160.0,
      "text": "Video: Which in turn belongs to a local group of galaxies."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 427160.0,
      "end_time": 429160.0,
      "text": "These form part of a grouping system"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 429160.0,
      "end_time": 432160.0,
      "text": "much as the stars do."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 432160.0,
      "end_time": 434160.0,
      "text": "They are so many and so varied that from this distance"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 434160.0,
      "end_time": 438160.0,
      "text": "they appear like the stars from Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 438160.0,
      "end_time": 441160.0,
      "text": "ED: You&#39;ve seen that film, and what&#39;s so great about this"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 441160.0,
      "end_time": 443160.0,
      "text": "whole conference is that everybody has been talking about scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 443160.0,
      "end_time": 445160.0,
      "text": "Everybody here is coming at it from a different way."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 445160.0,
      "end_time": 447160.0,
      "text": "I want to give you one example."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 447160.0,
      "end_time": 449160.0,
      "text": "E.O. Wilson once told me that when he looked at ants --"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 449160.0,
      "end_time": 452160.0,
      "text": "he loved them, of course, and he wanted to learn more about them --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 452160.0,
      "end_time": 454160.0,
      "text": "he consciously looked at them from the standpoint of scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 454160.0,
      "end_time": 456160.0,
      "text": "So here is the tiny creature."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 456160.0,
      "end_time": 458160.0,
      "text": "And yet simply by changing the frame of reference"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 458160.0,
      "end_time": 461160.0,
      "text": "it reveals so much, including what ended up being the TED Prize."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 461160.0,
      "end_time": 465160.0,
      "text": "Modeling, they tried modeling all the time. They were always modeling things."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 465160.0,
      "end_time": 468160.0,
      "text": "And I think part of that is that they never delegated understanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 468160.0,
      "end_time": 471160.0,
      "text": "And I think in our family we were very lucky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 471160.0,
      "end_time": 473160.0,
      "text": "because we learned about design backwards."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 473160.0,
      "end_time": 475160.0,
      "text": "Design was not something other."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 475160.0,
      "end_time": 477160.0,
      "text": "It was part of the business of life in general."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 477160.0,
      "end_time": 479160.0,
      "text": "It was part of the quality of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 479160.0,
      "end_time": 482160.0,
      "text": "And here is some family pictures."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 482160.0,
      "end_time": 484160.0,
      "text": "And you can see why I&#39;m down on style, with a haircut like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 484160.0,
      "end_time": 486160.0,
      "text": "But anyway, (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 486160.0,
      "end_time": 489160.0,
      "text": "I remember the cut grapefruit that we would have at the Eames house when I was a kid."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 489160.0,
      "end_time": 491160.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re going to watch another film."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 491160.0,
      "end_time": 494160.0,
      "text": "This is a film, the one called Toys."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 494160.0,
      "end_time": 498160.0,
      "text": "You can see me, I have the same haircut, in the upper right corner."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 498160.0,
      "end_time": 502160.0,
      "text": "Upper left is a film they did on toy trains."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 502160.0,
      "end_time": 505160.0,
      "text": "Lower right is a solar do-nothing toy."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 505160.0,
      "end_time": 508160.0,
      "text": "Lower left is Day-of-the-Dead toys."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 517159.0,
      "end_time": 520159.0,
      "text": "Charles used to say that toys are not as innocent as they appear."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 520159.0,
      "end_time": 524159.0,
      "text": "They are often the precursor to bigger things."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 524159.0,
      "end_time": 527160.0,
      "text": "And these ideas -- that train up there, being about the honest use of materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 527160.0,
      "end_time": 529160.0,
      "text": "is totally the same"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 529160.0,
      "end_time": 532160.0,
      "text": "as the honest use of materials in the plywood."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 536160.0,
      "end_time": 537160.0,
      "text": "And now I&#39;m going to test you."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 537160.0,
      "end_time": 541160.0,
      "text": "This is a letter that my grandfather sent to my mom when she was five years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 541160.0,
      "end_time": 543160.0,
      "text": "So can you read it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 543160.0,
      "end_time": 545160.0,
      "text": "Lucia angel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 545160.0,
      "end_time": 548160.0,
      "text": "okay, eye."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 548160.0,
      "end_time": 552160.0,
      "text": "Audience: Saw many trains."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 552160.0,
      "end_time": 557160.0,
      "text": "ED: Awl, also, good that the leather crafter&#39;s guild is here."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 557160.0,
      "end_time": 562160.0,
      "text": "Also, what is he doing? Row, rowed."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 562160.0,
      "end_time": 564160.0,
      "text": "Sun? No. Well is there another name for a sunrise?"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 564160.0,
      "end_time": 567160.0,
      "text": "Dawn, very good."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 567160.0,
      "end_time": 569160.0,
      "text": "Also rode on one. I ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 569160.0,
      "end_time": 571160.0,
      "text": "Audience: You had, I hope you had --"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 571160.0,
      "end_time": 573160.0,
      "text": "ED: Now you&#39;ve been to the website Dogs of Saint Louis"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 573160.0,
      "end_time": 575160.0,
      "text": "in the late, in the mid-1930&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 575160.0,
      "end_time": 577160.0,
      "text": "then you&#39;d know that was a Great Dane."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 577160.0,
      "end_time": 579160.0,
      "text": "So, I hope you had a"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 579160.0,
      "end_time": 583160.0,
      "text": "Audience: Nice time, time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 583160.0,
      "end_time": 585160.0,
      "text": "ED: Time at."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 585160.0,
      "end_time": 587160.0,
      "text": "Citizen Kane, rose --"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 587160.0,
      "end_time": 589160.0,
      "text": "Audience: Rosebud."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 589160.0,
      "end_time": 592160.0,
      "text": "ED: No, bud. \"D\"&#39;s right. At Buddy&#39;s --"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 592160.0,
      "end_time": 594160.0,
      "text": "Audience: Party. Love."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 594160.0,
      "end_time": 596160.0,
      "text": "ED: Okay, good."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 596160.0,
      "end_time": 598160.0,
      "text": "So, \"I saw many trains and also rode on one."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 598160.0,
      "end_time": 600160.0,
      "text": "I hope you had a nice time at Buddy&#39;s party.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 600160.0,
      "end_time": 603160.0,
      "text": "So you guys did pretty good, cool."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 603160.0,
      "end_time": 605160.0,
      "text": "So my mom and Charles had this great relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 605160.0,
      "end_time": 608160.0,
      "text": "where they&#39;d send those sorts of things back and forth to one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 608160.0,
      "end_time": 610160.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s all part of the, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 610160.0,
      "end_time": 612160.0,
      "text": "they used to say, \"Take your pleasure seriously.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 612160.0,
      "end_time": 615160.0,
      "text": "These are some images from a project of mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 615160.0,
      "end_time": 617160.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s called Kymaerica."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 617160.0,
      "end_time": 619160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s sort of an alternative universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 619160.0,
      "end_time": 622160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s kind of a reinterpretation of the landscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 622160.0,
      "end_time": 624160.0,
      "text": "Those plaques are plaques we&#39;ve been installing around North America."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 624160.0,
      "end_time": 627160.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re about to do six in the U.K. next week."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 627160.0,
      "end_time": 630160.0,
      "text": "And they honor events in the linear world from the fictional world."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 630160.0,
      "end_time": 632160.0,
      "text": "So, of course, since it&#39;s bronze it has to be true."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 632160.0,
      "end_time": 637160.0,
      "text": "Video: Kymaerica with waterfalls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 637160.0,
      "end_time": 639160.0,
      "text": "tumbling through our --"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 639160.0,
      "end_time": 641160.0,
      "text": "ED: This is one of the traditional Kymaerican songs."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 641160.0,
      "end_time": 646160.0,
      "text": "And so we had spelling bees in Paris, Illinois."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 646160.0,
      "end_time": 648160.0,
      "text": "Video: Your word is N. Carolina."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 648160.0,
      "end_time": 651160.0,
      "text": "Girl: Y-I-N-D-I-A-N-A."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 651160.0,
      "end_time": 655160.0,
      "text": "ED: And then Embassy Row is actually a historical site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 655160.0,
      "end_time": 657160.0,
      "text": "because in the Kymaerican story"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 657160.0,
      "end_time": 660160.0,
      "text": "this is where the Parisian Diaspora started, where there embassy was."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 660160.0,
      "end_time": 662160.0,
      "text": "So you can actually visit and have this three-dimensional"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 662160.0,
      "end_time": 664160.0,
      "text": "fictional experience there."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 664160.0,
      "end_time": 666160.0,
      "text": "And the town has really embraced it."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 666160.0,
      "end_time": 668160.0,
      "text": "We had the spelling bee in conjunction with the Gwomeus Club."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 668160.0,
      "end_time": 671160.0,
      "text": "But what is really cool is that we take our visual environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 671160.0,
      "end_time": 674160.0,
      "text": "as inevitable. And it&#39;s not."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 674160.0,
      "end_time": 677160.0,
      "text": "Other things could have happened. The Japanese could have discovered Monterey."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 677160.0,
      "end_time": 679160.0,
      "text": "And we could have been born 100,000 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 679160.0,
      "end_time": 681160.0,
      "text": "And there are a lot of fun things. This is the Museum of the Bench."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 681160.0,
      "end_time": 683160.0,
      "text": "They have trading cards"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 683160.0,
      "end_time": 685160.0,
      "text": "and all sorts of cool things."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 685160.0,
      "end_time": 689160.0,
      "text": "And you&#39;re kind of trapped in the texture of Kymaerica."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 689160.0,
      "end_time": 691160.0,
      "text": "The Tahatchabe, the great road building culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 691160.0,
      "end_time": 693160.0,
      "text": "A guy named Nobu Naga,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 693160.0,
      "end_time": 695160.0,
      "text": "the so-called Japanese Columbus."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 695160.0,
      "end_time": 697160.0,
      "text": "But now I&#39;m going to return you to the real world."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 697160.0,
      "end_time": 700160.0,
      "text": "And this is Cranbrook. I&#39;ve got a real treat for you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 700160.0,
      "end_time": 702160.0,
      "text": "which is the first film that Charles ever made."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 702160.0,
      "end_time": 705160.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s watch that. Nobody&#39;s ever seen it."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 705160.0,
      "end_time": 709160.0,
      "text": "Cranbrook is very generous to let us show it for the first time here."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 709160.0,
      "end_time": 713160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a film about Maya Gretel, a famous ceramicist, and a teacher at Cranbrook."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 713160.0,
      "end_time": 717160.0,
      "text": "And he made it for the 1939 faculty exhibition."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 717160.0,
      "end_time": 723160.0,
      "text": "Silent. We don&#39;t have a track for it yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 723160.0,
      "end_time": 726160.0,
      "text": "Very simple. It&#39;s just a start. But it&#39;s that learn-by-doing thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 726160.0,
      "end_time": 728160.0,
      "text": "You want to learn how to make films? Go make a movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 728160.0,
      "end_time": 730160.0,
      "text": "And you try something out."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 730160.0,
      "end_time": 732160.0,
      "text": "But here is what&#39;s really great."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 732160.0,
      "end_time": 736160.0,
      "text": "See that chair there? The orange one? That&#39;s the organic chair. 1940."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 736160.0,
      "end_time": 738160.0,
      "text": "At the same time that Charles was doing that chair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 738160.0,
      "end_time": 740160.0,
      "text": "he was doing this film."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 740160.0,
      "end_time": 742160.0,
      "text": "So my point is that this scope of vision, this holistic vision"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 742160.0,
      "end_time": 744160.0,
      "text": "of design, was with them from the beginning."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 744160.0,
      "end_time": 746160.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t like \"Oh, we made some chairs and got successful."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 746160.0,
      "end_time": 748160.0,
      "text": "Now we&#39;re going to do some movies.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 748160.0,
      "end_time": 751160.0,
      "text": "It was always part of how they looked at the world. And that&#39;s what&#39;s really powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 751160.0,
      "end_time": 754160.0,
      "text": "And I think that all of us in this room, as you move design forward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 754160.0,
      "end_time": 758160.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not about just doing one thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 758160.0,
      "end_time": 761160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about how you approach problems. And there is this huge, beautiful commonality"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 761160.0,
      "end_time": 764160.0,
      "text": "between design, business and the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 764160.0,
      "end_time": 766160.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re going to do the last clip."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 766160.0,
      "end_time": 768160.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ve shown you some of the images. I just want to focus on sound now."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 768160.0,
      "end_time": 770160.0,
      "text": "So this is Charles&#39; voice."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 770160.0,
      "end_time": 775160.0,
      "text": "Charles Eames: In India, those without, and the lowest in caste,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 775160.0,
      "end_time": 777160.0,
      "text": "eat very often, particularly in southern India,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 777160.0,
      "end_time": 780160.0,
      "text": "they eat off of a banana leaf."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 780160.0,
      "end_time": 784160.0,
      "text": "And those a little bit up the scale"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 784160.0,
      "end_time": 788160.0,
      "text": "eat off of a sort of a low-fired ceramic dish."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 788160.0,
      "end_time": 791160.0,
      "text": "And a little bit higher, why they have a glaze"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 791160.0,
      "end_time": 794160.0,
      "text": "on a thing they call a thali."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 794160.0,
      "end_time": 796160.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re up the scale a little bit more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 796160.0,
      "end_time": 798160.0,
      "text": "why, a brass thali."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 798160.0,
      "end_time": 802160.0,
      "text": "And then things get to be a little questionable."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 802160.0,
      "end_time": 805160.0,
      "text": "There are things like silver-plated thalis."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 805160.0,
      "end_time": 807160.0,
      "text": "And there is solid silver thalis."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 807160.0,
      "end_time": 810160.0,
      "text": "And I suppose some nut has had a"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 810160.0,
      "end_time": 812160.0,
      "text": "gold thali that he&#39;s eaten off of."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 812160.0,
      "end_time": 814160.0,
      "text": "But you can go beyond that."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 814160.0,
      "end_time": 819160.0,
      "text": "And the guys that have not only means,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 819160.0,
      "end_time": 824160.0,
      "text": "but a certain amount of knowledge and understanding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 824160.0,
      "end_time": 829160.0,
      "text": "go to the next step, and they eat off a banana leaf."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 829160.0,
      "end_time": 833160.0,
      "text": "And I think that in these times"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 833160.0,
      "end_time": 835160.0,
      "text": "when we fall back and regroup,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 835160.0,
      "end_time": 839160.0,
      "text": "that somehow or other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 839160.0,
      "end_time": 841160.0,
      "text": "the banana leaf parable"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 841160.0,
      "end_time": 843160.0,
      "text": "sort of got to get working there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 843160.0,
      "end_time": 846160.0,
      "text": "because I&#39;m not prepared to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 846160.0,
      "end_time": 849160.0,
      "text": "that the banana leaf that one eats off of"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 849160.0,
      "end_time": 854160.0,
      "text": "is the same as the other eats off of."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 854160.0,
      "end_time": 858160.0,
      "text": "But it is that process that has happened within the man"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 858160.0,
      "end_time": 861160.0,
      "text": "that changes the banana leaf."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 861160.0,
      "end_time": 863160.0,
      "text": "ED: I&#39;ve been looking forward to sharing that quote with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 863160.0,
      "end_time": 865160.0,
      "text": "Because that&#39;s part of where we&#39;ve got to get to."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 865160.0,
      "end_time": 867160.0,
      "text": "And I also want to share this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 867160.0,
      "end_time": 870160.0,
      "text": "\"Beyond the age of information is the age of choices.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 870160.0,
      "end_time": 872160.0,
      "text": "And I really think that&#39;s where we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 872160.0,
      "end_time": 875160.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s kind of cool for me to be part of a family"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 875160.0,
      "end_time": 878160.0,
      "text": "and a tradition where he was talking about that in 1978."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 878160.0,
      "end_time": 881160.0,
      "text": "And part of why this stuff is important"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 881160.0,
      "end_time": 883160.0,
      "text": "and all the things that we do are important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 883160.0,
      "end_time": 885160.0,
      "text": "is that these are the ideas we need."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 885160.0,
      "end_time": 888160.0,
      "text": "And I think that this is all part of surrendering to the design journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 888160.0,
      "end_time": 890160.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what we all need to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 890160.0,
      "end_time": 893160.0,
      "text": "Design is not just for designers anymore. It&#39;s a process. It&#39;s not style."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 893160.0,
      "end_time": 896160.0,
      "text": "All that great thinking needs to really get about solving"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 896160.0,
      "end_time": 898160.0,
      "text": "pretty key problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 898160.0,
      "end_time": 900160.0,
      "text": "I really thank you for your time."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 900160.0,
      "end_time": 903160.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}